WEBVTT

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:31.376
And he just sobered up immediately,

00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:33.416
and he stuck out his hand,

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.696
put a hand on my shoulder,

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:38.456
and in a real earnest,
very nice voice he was like,

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:39.861
"I hope you make it someday."

00:08:39.885 --> 00:08:41.765
(Laughter)

00:08:42.880 --> 00:08:44.080
And ...

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:49.296
I have so many moments like that
logged in my memory.

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:52.176
I just cringe thinking of that.

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:57.880
It's so embarrassing to just
not feel valued as a creative person.

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:00.736
But as a species,